209. Backchannel Message From the Ambassador to South Vietnam (Bunker) to the President’s Assistant
                    for National Security Affairs (Kissinger)Source:
                        Library of Congress, Manuscript Division, Kissinger Papers, Box TS 44,
                        Geopolitical File, Cables, Vietnam, 24 June–29 August 1972. Top Secret;
                        Sensitive; Immediate.
